  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Based on the reversal of the adverse cardiovascular parameters during Laproscopic Surgery and
      its influence on cardiac activity in healthy subjects, the investigators expect to improved
      cardiac function in patients suffering from congestive heart failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
